&lt;li&gt;Ability to manage a &lt;strong&gt;high-volume workload&lt;/strong&gt;, including ~30 inbound/outbound calls and ~20 emails daily, while consistently meeting SLA requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to &lt;strong&gt;multi-task &lt;/strong&gt;across phone and email channels simultaneously without impacting service quality.&lt;/li&gt;
